{"tid":1588723,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"以武制暴 - 重新審視","createTime":"2019-09-23T03:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T12:14:35.000Z","uid":260134,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d2a65db71e2e0e96768269329fd26de0e9f8e558","tid":1588723,"uid":260134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:01:59.000Z","msg":"先講明核爆都唔割，但係做法不完美，可改善。我諗大家都同意。<br />\n<br />\n今次係第一次我想大家諗清楚個方向。<br />\n之前機場之後大家都改咗用合照加64去處理，但係今次似乎係想繼續以武制暴。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意先唔講，外國見一班人打幾個平民look嘅人好容易大失民意。<br />\nSkynews都有播尋日沙田私了。（好大型嘅電視台）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Bk4P1oeItOA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBk4P1oeItOA&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=b60a1172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Bk4P1oeItOA</a><br />\n啲留言大家都睇到，我都相信唔只得佢哋會播。<br />\n<br />\n再係咁我哋會直接會完全被當係<span style=\"color: red;\">暴民</span>。<br />\n外國政府要正當性先容易做嘢，係香港人鬥極權。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而家我哋係邊緣化自己。</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好再講：唔了解成件事嘅人唔洗理。<br />\n因為從來非本地主流民意係睇形象同個故仔。<br />\n<br />\n所以唔係唔可以私，而係應該點樣私。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為：既然制服到，報警放人先係問題。<br />\n咁不如直接用索帶綁住，再留佢係果度算。<br />\n要做到：制服咗就唔郁手，示威者都做到，點解黑警做唔到？<br />\n<br />\n我哋話核彈都唔割，但係唔洗挑戰中立偏黃嘅底線，同埋要留意外國形象。<br />\n我知文宣會盡力，但係群眾打人從來就一定好難救形象。<br />\n<br />\n唔好因為藍絲挑機搞到變群眾鬥群眾。<span style=\"color: red;\">要全力對返個政權</span>。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"fc6b93acfcbf8f28135e20f40a00eff383f6f2fa","tid":1588723,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"c3160dcfd2513d7e86b7efc5c3c713c8f90c1cc7","tid":1588723,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:05:10.000Z","msg":"民意撚又出動了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勿推"},{"pid":"e831bd6bb7c95bdfd0b272ceef6d697f7e479230","tid":1588723,"uid":196949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"都係嗰句 你認為攞索帶索住啲廢老 有幾阻嚇？可唔可以阻嚇到佢以後都驚 唔再打人？"},{"pid":"7fac9b6bc21828301552ab435866f5e1aa8a39d5","tid":1588723,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:07:54.000Z","msg":"[（防禦）方向討論&amp;檢討]對家玩抹黑去掩蓋警暴，我地對應手法就係訂立界線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1588728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1588728</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1f33d1fc07606276425f571f4c76657085808b8e","tid":1588723,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:08:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"2430f912b54a4b20b88a50ded906b8a06b87c1db","tid":1588723,"uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:08:55.000Z","msg":"閱<br />\n可以唔洗推"},{"pid":"a0ac03fe9c552137f55608fbc8f9476a629fbb1d","tid":1588723,"uid":260134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3160dcfd2513d7e86b7efc5c3c713c8f90c1cc7","tid":1588723,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:05:10.000Z","msg":"民意撚又出動了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勿推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:12:00.000Z","msg":"一直都有文宣修正形象，你試下我哋同黑警相反文宣實力？<br />\n如果長期風氣係咁，文宣會救唔到。"},{"pid":"34974d38c7b5c4a16e52e6de1e05fdbe218ba4a5","tid":1588723,"uid":260134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e831bd6bb7c95bdfd0b272ceef6d697f7e479230","tid":1588723,"uid":196949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"都係嗰句 你認為攞索帶索住啲廢老 有幾阻嚇？可唔可以阻嚇到佢以後都驚 唔再打人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:17:56.000Z","msg":"呢個係我建議。<br />\n如果有阻嚇性就尋日點會又係沙田突多個？<br />\n如果中共要搞死我哋形象，係可以直接出錢比廢老出嚟挑機。<br />\n<br />\n外國整走抹黑示威者嘅Acc，呢啲會整到似外國幫緊我哋洗白。<br />\n<br />\n一係就文宣同外國人解釋（如果佢哋接受/得閒去諗咁多），一係就我哋改方式。<br />\n<br />\n藍絲搞事一定要處理得啱。"},{"pid":"8902da52220ed9ac387622d8dd5cf799ec971fd9","tid":1588723,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e831bd6bb7c95bdfd0b272ceef6d697f7e479230","tid":1588723,"uid":196949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"都係嗰句 你認為攞索帶索住啲廢老 有幾阻嚇？可唔可以阻嚇到佢以後都驚 唔再打人？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:29:13.000Z","msg":"靠武力阻嚇廢老？<br />\n黑警又何嘗唔想用濫暴阻嚇示威者？"},{"pid":"d748c1b8e7e44b18a6d58e9a66892edf78172b94","tid":1588723,"uid":196949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8902da52220ed9ac387622d8dd5cf799ec971fd9","tid":1588723,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e831bd6bb7c95bdfd0b272ceef6d697f7e479230","tid":1588723,"uid":196949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"都係嗰句 你認為攞索帶索住啲廢老 有幾阻嚇？可唔可以阻嚇到佢以後都驚 唔再打人？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:29:13.000Z","msg":"靠武力阻嚇廢老？<br />\n黑警又何嘗唔想用濫暴阻嚇示威者？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:38:32.000Z","msg":"死廢老肯定係有抗爭者意志咁堅定 不惜犧牲一切代價都要打人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb30edb7283d164a8e410088b8e86f2edf5aa3f","tid":1588723,"uid":196949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8902da52220ed9ac387622d8dd5cf799ec971fd9","tid":1588723,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e831bd6bb7c95bdfd0b272ceef6d697f7e479230","tid":1588723,"uid":196949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"都係嗰句 你認為攞索帶索住啲廢老 有幾阻嚇？可唔可以阻嚇到佢以後都驚 唔再打人？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:29:13.000Z","msg":"靠武力阻嚇廢老？<br />\n黑警又何嘗唔想用濫暴阻嚇示威者？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:39:32.000Z","msg":"邊個欺善怕惡 邊個寧願死都要保衛 唔係要講得咁白先明吖話？"},{"pid":"8c2732bef48c83aff306d283a459a63295706116","tid":1588723,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:01:15.000Z","msg":"【 9.28 + 10.1 】連發宣傳<br />\n<br />\n五年前的9月28日，催淚彈劃破夏愨道的半空，開展一場劍指真普選的佔領運動。<br />\n<br />\n五年過去，真普選雖仍遙遙無期，而警察比以前更黑、更暴力、更不受監管。但是，香港人履行了在當日佔領結束時許下的承諾 －「人民誓將歸來」。五年後的香港人，以更團結、更鏗鏘、更堅毅的姿態再次站到政權的面前，對抗警暴，爭取雙真普選。<br />\n<br />\n9月28日，作為一個我們都記得；我們都認為是重要的日子 － 雨傘運動五周年，我們希望和大家一同回到金鐘，在集會當中沉澱、思考。<br />\n<br />\n同時，縱然當前要舉辦一個合法的遊行是會被多番刁難，而部份手足亦已經視不反對通知書為廢紙，但我們仍入紙希望可以舉辦10.1遊行，盡力讓當日能夠有一個讓所有香港人都能夠參與的大遊行，因此約定大家，十月一日，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n【 9.28 反抗威權 迎接黎明 】集會<br />\n2019年9月28日<br />\n晚上7時至9時<br />\n金鐘添馬公園<br />\n<br />\n【 10.1 沒有國慶 只有國殤 】遊行<br />\n2019年10月1日<br />\n下午兩時起步<br />\n維園集合，遊行往遮打道<br />\n<br />\n主辦︰民間人權陣線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8Dkz2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8Dkz2M.jpg&h=c7d62bd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qS9jQCv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqS9jQCv.jpg&h=769335de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hqy41Ka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqy41Ka.jpg&h=a6dbaf1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJQZQCw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJQZQCw.jpg&h=ba39fbf6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aba798a0b6a0e5525f939a6a621e73b5ebd3b14e","tid":1588723,"uid":260134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cb30edb7283d164a8e410088b8e86f2edf5aa3f","tid":1588723,"uid":196949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8902da52220ed9ac387622d8dd5cf799ec971fd9","tid":1588723,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e831bd6bb7c95bdfd0b272ceef6d697f7e479230","tid":1588723,"uid":196949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"都係嗰句 你認為攞索帶索住啲廢老 有幾阻嚇？可唔可以阻嚇到佢以後都驚 唔再打人？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:29:13.000Z","msg":"靠武力阻嚇廢老？<br />\n黑警又何嘗唔想用濫暴阻嚇示威者？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:39:32.000Z","msg":"邊個欺善怕惡 邊個寧願死都要保衛 唔係要講得咁白先明吖話？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:14:35.000Z","msg":"問題係成班人去毆打兩個平民裝。如果次次係咁點搞？"}]}